indicador: Gap in desired fertility between spouses - DHS
detalle_indicador: Difference in the desired number of children between the male and female of a couple. The reference population includes women aged 25 to 49 years in heterosexual couples.
disclaimer: The series may present jumps due to methodological changes in the surveys (see methodological documents). Source: GenLAC (CEDLAS).
